headline: Glenfarne, Baker Hughes Announce Definitive Agreements to Advance Alaska LNG
summary: WASHINGTON, November 10, 2025--Glenfarne and Baker Hughes announce definitive agreements for Alaska LNG in a ceremony in Washington, DC.

headline: Nat-Gas Prices Gain on Colder US Weather Forecasts
summary: December Nymex natural gas (NGZ25 ) on Monday closed up +0.023 (+0.53%). Dec nat-gas prices rallied to an 8-month nearest-futures high on Monday as forecasts for colder US temperatures could boost heating demand for nat-gas.
